values:
Tomorrow, I will have 20 years old. I'm old, isn't he ?
All people say to me "I didn't think that you have already 20. I thought you had 17 or 18" Then, they made a strange face.
What's the problem with my age ?
I know I'm late in my schooling but now I'm in my last year of College and I will have my bac and I will go to university !
If you don't love my age, I just want to say "FUCK !"

Today I saw my dad in my grandma's house. He was so fool !
My grandma gave me 150 euros. My dad will give me my money tomorrow (He said but I don't believe him, I don't know why... *ironic*) He just said "You have many spots !" and I said "Hello Dad, thank to be so nice with your poor daughter !"
I never see a foolish man than him ! Fucking dad ! Moreover I have not spots, I have scar of my spots !
I didn't say to him "Oh God ! I think that your stomach is so full, make a diet !"
If my english is a problem fuck  you !
